{"tid":113533,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打玩 stereo photography?","createTime":"2017-02-09T05:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T14:15:10.000Z","uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3b755d697beff481659e9cd1a7ca239202e0cc","tid":113533,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:06:53.000Z","msg":"最近影貓覺得影完同實際畫象感覺始終唔同<br />\n無左立體感<br />\n所以搵左下 stereo photography既資料<br />\n原來 stereo photography出過既 camera都唔好夠賣做唔住<br />\n我諗如果真係要紀錄一個畫面更有真實感覺，立體感好緊要，特別係影近而又形狀多detail既野更明顯<br />\n將來vr變得更普及，睇stereo photo或 video會更方便，所以想打探下你地點玩<br />\n<br />\nBtw如果部手機夠寬，一左一右 camera已經拍到 stereo不過好似未有廠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0c62d5b7ac8db6bb15c7588d3870ee74b0a2d9","tid":113533,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"諗落手機都唔一定駛寬身，鏡頭一上一下都ok，有人左右眼距離效果就明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949ecc944813683955574bdc5a147be4a36cf7d1","tid":113533,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}